<<dialog "player">>No, thankfully that's never happened.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "neighborMia">>Good. I hope it never does. But if it ever happens, tell me, okay? I'm here for you.<</dialog>>
    <</replace>>
    <<rememberChar "neighborMia" "player_unwanted_touch" "no" "personal" "Mia asked about unwanted touch">>
<</btn>>
<<btn "I don't want to talk about it.">>
